1601697600.title: CNN Newsroom
1601697600.descr: CNN Newroom provides the most up to date news as it breaks and is the longest running show on the channel, airing twice a day Monday to Friday and throughout the day over the weekends. CNN was founding in 1980 by American media proprietor Ted Turner as a 24 hour cable news channel and has since won multiple media awards.

1601698500.title: Marketplace Africa
1601698500.descr: Marketplace Africa on CNN offers unique access to the latest African market information, with a look at events and developments that impact its business world. Eleni Giokos is the show's host. Every week she interviews figures of business and industry to reveal the economic trends in various regions of Africa and to present the continent's key sectors and corporations.

1601699400.title: Inside Africa
1601699400.descr: Each week, Inside Africa documentary series on CNN highlights the unique diversity of mysterious Africa, its numerous cultures and religions, peoples, art, music, cuisine, travel and literature, its one-of-a-kind flora and fauna. Everything what Africa is filled with and lives for is in this series.

1601701200.title: Tech for Good
1601701200.descr: The power of technology to build a better world – incredible people beating the odds to follow their dreams, and the remarkable new technologies enabling them and others to thrive.
